            "last_activity_date": 1366670136,
            "creation_date": 1366670136,
            "body": "<p>from performance point of view does not matter as there is always small number of HTTP parameters. <\/p>\n\n<p>Personally i like this way : <\/p>\n\n<pre><code> new Uri.Builder()\n.scheme(\"http\")\n.authority(\"foo.com\")\n.path(\"someservlet\")\n.appendQueryParameter(\"param1\", foo)\n.appendQueryParameter(\"param2\", bar)\n.build();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
